t: "If you ask them ňĻO Prophetňļ who created the heavens and the earth, they will certainly say, ‚ÄúGod!‚ÄĚ Ask ňĻthemňļ, ‚ÄúConsider then whatever ňĻidolsňļ you invoke besides God: if it was God‚Äôs Will to harm me, could they undo that harm? Or if He willed ňĻsomeňļ mercy for me, could they withhold His mercy?‚ÄĚ Say, ‚ÄúGod is sufficient for me. In Him ňĻaloneňļ the faithful put their trust.‚ÄĚ"